# Randomit ðŸŽ²

A Python library to generate random things.

[![codecov coverage](https://codecov.io/gh/dimitryzub/randomit/branch/main/graph/badge.svg?token=B2XA8Y3R5M)](https://codecov.io/gh/dimitryzub/randomit)
